job.title: MPPSC Medical Officer Recruitment 2021  Apply Online for 576 vacancies in Madhya Pradesh
job.body:
Total vacancies:576

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Medial Officer 

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Doctors has been published by Madhya Pradesh Public Service Commission for Medial Officer vacancies in Madhya Pradesh. If you are searching for a government job in Madhya Pradesh then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Medical Officer, from 24-06-2021, and till 23-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Madhya Pradesh and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for SC, ST, OBC & PWD Candidates of MP State category candidates is only Rs. 250/-
  • The application fee for Others Candidates of MP State category candidates is only Rs. 500/-

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Medical Officer  in MPPSC, your MBBS must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 24-06-2021 
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 23-07-2021 

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 40 years old. 

MPPSC Medical Officer Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly

salary is as per norms

How to apply for MPPSC Medical Officer Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Medical Officer. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of MPPSC and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by MPPSC
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
